\begin_inset Formula $A^{3}=I$
\end_inset

.
 Because the subgroup 
\begin_inset Formula $\{I,\,A,\,A^{2}\}$
\end_inset

 would have three elements which is not a factor of 
\begin_inset Formula $4$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
